00:10:20.154 --> 00:10:22.356 position:41% line:83% align:start
YOTALU:
Such a tragic sight.

00:10:23.324 --> 00:10:26.127 position:21% line:83% align:start
Is it really the work
of Aquafa loyalists?

00:10:26.160 --> 00:10:30.698 position:7% line:83% align:start
